				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				<BR>
What is with all of these debates? realy?<BR>
EACH class is nessisary, each class has its uses.<BR>
<BR>
Meele does damage and protects casters<BR>
<BR>
Casters attack from affar and heal/buff the Meele<BR>
<BR>
Hybrid do a little of both by assisting the meele and casting the lesser spells so the casters can spend mana on the better spells<BR>
<BR>
Guess where we bards fall in the grand scheme? were hybrids... the ultimate... the TRUE hybrid... we have traits from most of the classes.. we were designed to be complementary to almost any group.  what? chanter OOM? ok... ill mez the mob till he has enough mana.  War seriously hurt? pull em back and let me step in, ill hold my own till he can return to the frey...<BR>
<BR>
stop busting each other over whos the BEST.  Cause guess what? there is NO BEST. <BR>
&quot;B..but... I got all these nifty things&quot; you might say...  well  whoopty-friggin-doooo...<BR>
<BR>
you are not the only one with that spiffy armor/weapon/spell <BR>
and many classes have innate defences against what they cannot use.<BR>
<BR>
Dont spazz over who has the shiniest armor or the lighest boots. cause all that nifty equipment wont be worth 1CP if you cant play your character worth a... well... you get the idea...(Or atleast SHOULD be getting it by now.. lol)<BR>
<BR>
dont tease somebody because you think their class sucks... because you never know when that &quot;crappy&quot; class will save your butt!<BR>
<BR>
I remember back in my days of hunting orcs in oasis.. there was a warrior in my group that wouldnt stop making fun of bards.  well, one day a sand giant came over the nearest dune and proceeded to slaughter the group next to us.... our group scattered.  everybody ran in a different direction... I and two others got as far as the gypsies when i saw the warior's health start plumeting... i told the two to contunue to zone... I turned back, flicked out my drums and ran to his side... i told him to follow me closely. well, i got him to zone and regened those of us that made it.  we've become prety good friends now. he dosent make fun of other class/races...  now he only makes fun about one class... his own... and rightfully so... The only thing you have a right to make fun of is YOURSELF<BR>
<BR>
alot of EQ players need to take a close look at themselves.  Are they playing the game because they think its fun? or are they playing just to aquire that shiny new -Insert Item Name- ?<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Think about it....<BR>
<BR>

